CONTRIBUTIONS
Contributions are accepted via pull requests in the GitHub repository.
Follow strict TypeScript code standards (avoid any unless justified).
Prefer predictable functional logic.
Ensure all tests pass by running npm test.
Use Conventional Commits for commit messages (e.g., feat, fix, chore, docs).
Please report security vulnerabilities privately via email or the provided security channels; do not create public issues for security flaws.

